## PROPS:

-I created one resto-card , now i want resto-cards that doesnt mean i have to print that resto card everytime..
-I can do this by creating props.
-Props are like arguments given in a function , but in the case of react it is component.
-It is a JS object , so it has to be given as an argument in the component.

