## CLEARING UP THE FOLDER:

-I created an other folder "src" adn moved app.js into it and made changes in script line of html
-Create component folder in src and many other files can be added , to create sepeatee folder for each component.
-When a heading file is created in src , when we do that , there is no heading in app.js , so it throws an error , to correct it we have to export and then import it.
-export default Heading; (use this in heading file only)
-import it in app.js, "import Header from "./components/Heading.js";"
-Never put your hard coded in components folder(industrial advice).
-All the images link , url can be added into seperate file called utils.
-export default allows you to write only once in the file , to do multiple exports used named exports.
-To import named ones use { } these brackets.

