## Virtual DOM

- A JS-based copy of the real DOM

React uses it To perform efficient UI updates

## React Fiber

- The engine that makes rendering smarter, faster, and interruptible

## Reconciliation Algorithm

- Compares old vs new VDOM and updates real DOM efficiently

