## Link component:

-If i click about us , home ....then it opens a new fresh page everytime as we are using , href link (anchor tag), which is a bad method.
-Instead usage of this link component makes it easy by not loading the whole page , which makes our application faster.
-works like anchor tag.
-Firstly , import link tag from react-dom.
-And then use it in the tags , using link component.
-Becuz of this , react applications are called as single page applications.

